Your health will regenerate if you don't get hit for a while

Rewards for slaining monsters: 

IMP  + Health
GOB  + Health
VAM  + Attack
ZOM  + Defense
SPI  + Max Health
LIC  + Attack, Health, Max Power (rare)

q - unleash the Ginger Power. Depletes the power bar. Damage and area of
effect depends on the number of charges

Press 'c' to continue
